### Why MongoConfig is NOT deleted here (CORRECTED from earlier draft)

Earlier drafts of this bead deleted `MongoConfig.java` here. That was wrong:

- Slice 2 (`nail-art-61s.3`) excluded Spring Boot Mongo autoconfig. With autoconfig disabled, `MongoConfig.java` is the ONLY source of `MongoTemplate` / `MongoClient` beans.
