- Deleting `MongoConfig.java` at slice 6 would break the dev API immediately after merge — every Appointment endpoint fails to wire on boot.

**Correct placement**: MongoConfig deletion lives in slice 9 (`nail-art-rs7.1`) alongside the Mongo dependency removal and Counter deletion. That is the moment NO `@Document` entities remain in the codebase.

